data.description: Looking for a great starter home or ready to downsize? LOOK NO MORE! This single story home has so much to offer! This home has spacious bedrooms and an office with NO carpet in sight! There is also nobody directly behind you! Only a short walk to the community pool, playground, jogging trails and sport courts. The home is located minutes away from Sea World, Lackland, AFB and plenty of shopping and dining. Come and see it today!
